longBusinessSummary: Golden Cariboo Resources Ltd., an exploration stage junior mining company, engages in the identification, acquisition, and exploration of mineral properties in Canada. The company holds interest in the Quesnelle Gold Quartz Mine property, which includes 20 mineral claims covering 3,794.8 hectares located in the Cariboo Mining Division of British Columbia. Golden Cariboo Resources Ltd. was incorporated in 1987 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
